<p>MIPS has an instruction to do <code>blt</code> (branch if less than). For example:</p>  <pre><code>blt $t0, $t1,target  #branch to target if $t0&lt;=$t1.   </code></pre>  <p>I want to know how to do this same operation using only Equal or Not Equal: </p>  <pre><code>bne $rt, $rs, target #Branch to target if $a0 and $a1 are NOT equal </code></pre>  <p>or</p>  <pre><code>beq $rt, $rs, target #Branch to target if $a0 and $a1 are equal </code></pre>